          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>soy sauce</strong> to a bowl with your <strong>mirin</strong>, <strong>sriracha </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>cornflour</strong> and 4 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[6 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[8 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water </strong>and mix until smooth – this is your <strong>spicy soy sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1583418208419-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
