            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Rinse your <strong>blanched</strong> <strong>edamame beans</strong> under <strong>cold running water</strong></p><p>Once the carrot<strong> </strong>has softened, add the<strong> edamame beans </strong>and <strong>spicy soy sauce </strong>to the pan and cook for 2-3 min<strong> </strong>until everything is warmed through and fully coated in the sauce – this is your <strong>veggie udon stir-fry</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
