        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>veggie udon stir-fry</strong> with a <strong>sesame fried egg</strong> on top</p><p>Tear over your <strong>coriander </strong>and top with a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong> and any <strong>remaining black sesame seeds </strong>from the pan</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
